                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.115/324</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">El Paso</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-07-07T12:00:00-07:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 7, 1917, noon</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Repayment promised July 15, but promise is not believed. Merchants there greatly
                    depressed by increasing excessive business tax in addition to general loan.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Cobb</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
